name: Blasphemy against the second law of thermodynamics, No.1
description: The irreversibility of time is broken. Our past is someone else's future and their future is our past. The causality is broken, the entropy is fixed and the mind is unable to comprehend. This is the first piece of the "Blasphemy against the second law of thermodynamics" collection. enjoy! @smjtyazdi, https://www.instagram.com/smjty.art/
